## Testing Standards

- Backend: `pytest` with `httpx` async test client
- Frontend: `Vitest` + `React Testing Library`
- Mobile: `Jest` + `Detox` for E2E
- Minimum coverage target: 70% on services layer
- All new API endpoints require at least one happy-path and one error-path test

-----

## Claude Code Session Protocol

1. **Read this file first** at the start of every session
1. **Update WIP section** if tasks are completed or new ones added
1. **Work in feature branches** — never commit directly to `main`
1. **Scope changes per session** — one module or feature at a time
1. **Do not modify infra files** without explicit instruction from Stephen
1. **Reference `docs/` for architecture decisions** before proposing structural changes

-----

## Out of Scope for This Repo

This repo is **OpsAI only**. The following are separate projects with their own repos and CLAUDE.md files:

- `BidShield AI` — proposal-to-contract tool for contractors
- `Trading Dashboard` — personal trading/options dashboard (Tiingo, Tradier, covered call logic)

Do not cross-reference or apply patterns from those projects here unless explicitly told to.